    <abstract>
      <t>RFC5420 extends RSVP-TE to specify or record generic attributes which apply to the whole of the path of an LSP. This document proposes an extension to the RSVP ERO and RRO objects to allow it to specify or record generic attributes which apply to a given hop.</t>
